Can't you say something useful?

13
00:01:33,150 --> 00:01:34,930
Didn't you just go inquire about it?

14
00:01:34,930 --> 00:01:36,030
Your Highness,

15
00:01:36,070 --> 00:01:37,190
I did.

16
00:01:37,370 --> 00:01:39,229
His Majesty rarely visits the harem.

17
00:01:39,229 --> 00:01:40,350
It seems

18
00:01:40,390 --> 00:01:41,420
he's not into women.

19
00:01:41,420 --> 00:01:42,570
But the consorts

20
00:01:42,590 --> 00:01:43,590
