25
00:01:56,090 --> 00:01:57,060
We're

26
00:01:57,090 --> 00:01:59,729
short by 128 taels of silver here.

27
00:02:00,650 --> 00:02:01,690
I kept quiet

28
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:02,920
to save your dignity.

29
00:02:03,190 --> 00:02:04,070
But you're getting

30
00:02:04,070 --> 00:02:05,470
