31
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:17,380
Remember to open the windows.

32
00:02:40,570 --> 00:02:41,770
No slacking off.

33
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,750
Keep up with me.

34
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:43,990
Let's do it again.

35
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:46,000
Ready,

36
00:02:46,150 --> 00:02:47,190
go!

37
