a man of the martial world.

42
00:02:55,850 --> 00:02:56,860
His martial arts skills are superb.

43
00:02:56,860 --> 00:02:57,329
We...

44
00:02:57,350 --> 00:02:59,079
Even if it costs me everything,

45
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,510
I'll kill him.

46
00:03:02,410 --> 00:03:03,270
Back then,

47
00:03:03,270 --> 00:03:05,390
my father led troops to support him.

48
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:06,670
But at the critical moment,

49
00:03:06,670 --> 00:03:07,690
he abandoned my father

50
00:03:07,690 --> 00:03:09,820
and refused to send troops to save him.

51
00:03:10,050 --> 00:03:11,230
What a scoundrel.

52
00:03:13,110 --> 00:03:15,520
If he had even a shred of humanity,

53
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:17,360
my father wouldn't have died.

54
00:03:17,380 --> 00:03:17,960
A man like that

55
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,360
doesn't deserve to live.

56
00:03:19,900 --> 00:03:21,310
Your Highness, don't worry.

57
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,070
There might be

58
00:03:22,070 --> 00:03:23,190
a chance you can

59
00:03:23,220 --> 00:03:24,510
use to your advantage.

60
00:03:24,890 --> 00:03:25,990
What is it?

61
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:29,870
His Majesty favors only

62
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:32,410
Consort Yue in Fengluan Palace.

63
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,190
Consort Yue?

64
00:03:35,350 --> 00:03:36,300
He favors only her?

65
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,270
Yes.

66
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:43,160
His Majesty is not easy to approach.

67
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:45,570
Getting close to this favored consort

68
00:03:46,010 --> 00:03:48,070
