75
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:08,230
Alright,

76
00:04:08,260 --> 00:04:08,880
Your Majesty.

77
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:10,540
Stop putting food on my plate.

78
00:04:11,350 --> 00:04:12,550
