83
00:04:23,030 --> 00:04:24,790
You should eat more.

84
00:04:25,050 --> 00:04:26,910
You're about to die from illness.

85
00:04:28,730 --> 00:04:30,030
Quick,

86
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:31,030
