90
00:04:36,150 --> 00:04:36,950
You two...

91
00:04:36,990 --> 00:04:38,630
You two must

92
00:04:38,659 --> 00:04:39,990
keep me safe.

93
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:42,510
One is your brother,

94
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:44,030
and the other is your…

95
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:49,070
You don't trust us?

96
00:04:52,550 --> 00:04:55,190
One is my brother...

97
00:04:57,020 --> 00:04:59,310
And what is the other one to me?

98
00:04:59,970 --> 00:05:01,070
Tell me.

99
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,190
Just eat.

100
00:05:11,110 --> 00:05:12,310
I heard

101
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:14,280
Wen Rou moved into Qunyu Pavilion.

102
00:05:14,670 --> 00:05:15,550
Your Majesty,

103
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:17,610
when do you plan to make her a consort?

104
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:25,750
I also heard that Wen Rou,

105
00:05:25,790 --> 00:05:26,870
a girl as beautiful

106
00:05:26,910 --> 00:05:28,110
as a flower,

107
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,670
is extremely attentive

108
00:05:29,670 --> 00:05:32,430
and eager

109
00:05:32,580 --> 00:05:34,550
to serve Your Majesty.

110
00:05:35,770 --> 00:05:37,110
That's true.

111
00:05:37,690 --> 00:05:39,310
Wen Rou isn't like you.

112
00:05:39,590 --> 00:05:40,310
What's wrong with me?

113
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:41,430
What's wrong with me?

114
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:42,430
You're gentle too.

115
00:05:42,430 --> 00:05:43,590
You're gentle too.

116
00:05:46,570 --> 00:05:49,430
I've been staying up late

117
00:05:49,810 --> 00:05:51,070
reviewing memorials,

118
00:05:51,450 --> 00:05:53,180
and my shoulders are a bit sore.

119
00:05:53,630 --> 00:05:55,890
Dear, would you please give me a massage?

120
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:58,880
These past few days,

121
00:05:58,950 --> 00:06:00,750
I've been practicing embroidery,

122
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:02,900
and my shoulders and neck are really sore.

123
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:04,230
Your Majesty, how about you

124
00:06:04,230 --> 00:06:05,560
give me a massage first?

125
00:06:08,550 --> 00:06:11,150
Your Highness, let me help you.

126
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:13,210
Yue,

127
00:06:13,230 --> 00:06:14,110
let me do it.

128
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:15,310
I have strong hands.

129
00:06:20,710 --> 00:06:22,070
Where does it hurt?

130
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:23,570
Everywhere hurts.

131
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,910
How about here?

132
00:06:27,290 --> 00:06:28,710
Can you press harder?

133
00:06:28,740 --> 00:06:29,910
Harder?

134
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,010
How's that, Dear?

135
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,950
Very good.

136
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,190
Yue.

137
00:06:51,790 --> 00:06:52,650
Your Highness.

138
00:06:53,030 --> 00:06:53,560
Coming.

139
00:06:54,450 --> 00:06:55,520
Has His Majesty left?

140
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,470
He has been at court for a while now.

141
00:06:56,470 --> 00:06:57,800
What time is it already?

142
00:06:59,530 --> 00:07:00,550
Let me tell you,

143
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:01,950
I read another

144
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:04,010
super interesting novel last night.

145
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:06,680
I just stayed up a bit late reading it.

146
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:08,290
Your Highness,

147
00:07:08,290 --> 00:07:09,750
let's have breakfast.

148
00:07:10,030 --> 00:07:11,370
His Majesty specially ordered

149
00:07:11,370 --> 00:07:12,770
it to be kept warm for you.

150
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,950
Ling'er, are you here?

151
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,530
I'm Wen Rou.

152
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:25,110
Greetings, Ling'er.

153
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:26,910
I apologize for my rudeness.

154
00:07:26,910 --> 00:07:27,870
I haven't visited you

155
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:29,510
since I came to the palace.

156
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:32,870
So you're Wen Rou.

157
00:07:34,980 --> 00:07:37,310
You really are very gentle.

158
00:07:37,770 --> 00:07:38,670
Actually,

159
00:07:38,670 --> 00:07:40,790
you're a bit older than me.

160
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:42,780
You can just call me Ling'er.

161
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,190
You live up to your name too.

162
00:07:45,230 --> 00:07:46,960
I liked you the moment I saw you.

163
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:48,680
I came to visit you today

164
00:07:48,810 --> 00:07:50,460
but I don't have anything presentable.

165
00:07:50,460 --> 00:07:51,460
So I just made some

166
00:07:51,470 --> 00:07:52,930
homemade local dishes
from the Northern Commandery.

167
00:07:52,930 --> 00:07:55,510
Please don't laugh
if they're not well made.

168
00:07:57,630 --> 00:07:58,550
I won't.

169
00:08:01,810 --> 00:08:02,990
Did you...

170
00:08:03,020 --> 00:08:04,830
make all these yourself?

171
00:08:07,870 --> 00:08:08,990
Oh my goodness.

172
00:08:09,470 --> 00:08:11,520
You haven't eaten breakfast yet, right?

173
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,980
How about we eat together?

174
00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:13,950
Alright.

175
00:08:15,170 --> 00:08:16,900
Then I won't stand on ceremony.

176
00:08:26,970 --> 00:08:28,540
This is delicious too.

177
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,270
Oh, I lost.

178
00:08:46,450 --> 00:08:48,630
Your chess skills are amazing.

179
00:08:49,130 --> 00:08:50,270
It was just luck.

180
00:08:50,490 --> 00:08:53,090
I can't believe someone said
I'm good at chess.

181
00:08:54,660 --> 00:08:56,390
The Empress Dowager is here!

182
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:03,910
The small kitchen

183
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:04,540
made some braised dishes.

184
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:05,390
I specially had them

185
00:09:05,390 --> 00:09:06,310
sent over.

186
00:09:06,490 --> 00:09:07,910
Your Majesty, you are so kind to me,

187
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:08,790
even kinder

188
00:09:08,810 --> 00:09:09,840
than my own brother.

189
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,750
Of course I am.

190
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:11,910
Eunuch Wang.

191
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:13,900
Yue,

192
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:15,720
go pour some tea for Her Majesty.

193
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:17,160
Yes, Your Highness.

194
00:09:26,740 --> 00:09:28,230
I've been wondering.

195
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:29,790
Ever since Wen Rou got here,

196
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:32,180
Consort Yue hasn't come
to visit me anymore.

197
00:09:32,180 --> 00:09:33,370
Everyone says

198
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,520
there's a young girl

199
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:36,340
in Fengluan Palace who keeps Consort Yue

200
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:36,990
company every day.

201
00:09:36,990 --> 00:09:38,870
So that's you, Wen Rou.

202
00:09:38,910 --> 00:09:39,670
Haha.

203
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:41,800
Ling'er and I hit it off right away.

204
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:43,150
And with

205
00:09:43,190 --> 00:09:45,340
the care from you and His Majesty,

206
00:09:45,370 --> 00:09:47,310
it really feels like home now.

207
00:09:48,510 --> 00:09:49,470
That's good.

208
00:09:49,870 --> 00:09:51,070
I'm glad to hear that.

209
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:54,460
Mother, please don't be angry.

210
00:09:54,490 --> 00:09:56,070
It's all my fault.

211
00:09:58,410 --> 00:09:59,670
Where is your consort?

212
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,510
Her Highness is playing chess

213
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:02,770
with Princess Wen Rou.

214
00:10:02,860 --> 00:10:04,660
The Empress Dowager is here too.

215
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:06,070
Wen Rou again?

216
00:10:06,690 --> 00:10:07,710
Didn't they just go flower viewing

217
00:10:07,710 --> 00:10:08,950
together yesterday?

218
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:10,990
Princess Wen Rou comes every day,

219
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:12,430
almost as often as you do.

220
00:10:17,340 --> 00:10:18,350
I'll brew some

221
00:10:18,350 --> 00:10:19,030
new plum wine

222
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:19,970
and send it to you.

223
00:10:19,970 --> 00:10:21,270
It goes perfectly with the braised dishes.

224
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:22,510
Let me serve you some now.

225
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:23,430
Wait.

226
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:26,770
I'm abstaining from alcohol and meat now.

227
00:10:26,790 --> 00:10:27,790
Because tomorrow,

228
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:30,450
I'm going to Cheng'en Temple
to worship Buddha.

229
00:10:32,140 --> 00:10:33,110
I didn't expect you

230
00:10:33,110 --> 00:10:34,790
to be so devout.

231
00:10:34,820 --> 00:10:36,420
Then why did you bring so much

232
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,430
pig's head meat and pork knuckles?

233
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:40,370
I heard you ate

234
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,570
a lot of them too.

235
00:10:41,590 --> 00:10:42,270
Shut up.

236
00:10:43,490 --> 00:10:45,660
I'm only starting it tomorrow.

237
00:10:47,430 --> 00:10:51,510
Besides, wine and meat
pass through the intestines,

238
00:10:51,530 --> 00:10:54,190
but Buddha stays in my heart forever.

239
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:03,910
Pour me some wine.

240
00:11:04,900 --> 00:11:05,830
Sir,

241
00:11:06,090 --> 00:11:08,180
we're about to close.

242
00:11:11,430 --> 00:11:12,910
You've been rushing us all along.

243
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,390
What's the rush?

244
00:11:15,380 --> 00:11:17,180
Do I look like I don't have money,

245
00:11:18,540 --> 00:11:20,400
or like I haven't given you money?

246
00:11:25,710 --> 00:11:26,910
Do you even know

247
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:28,560
who I am?

248
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:31,860
Please, keep drinking.

249
00:11:31,860 --> 00:11:32,830
Please enjoy.

250
00:11:34,060 --> 00:11:35,030
Your Highness,

251
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:37,120
we should keep a low profile.

252
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:38,660
Although the situation recently

253
00:11:38,660 --> 00:11:40,320
isn't as tense as it was before,

254
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,120
after all,

255
00:11:41,140 --> 00:11:42,600
this isn't our territory.

256
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:47,660
What am I afraid of?

257
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:50,150
Am I afraid of Huo Jingheng?

258
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:51,770
Or...

259
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:54,840
Yue Chi?

260
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:56,850
Keep your voice down,

261
00:11:56,850 --> 00:11:57,780
Your Highness.

262
00:12:01,310 --> 00:12:02,870
I've arranged everything.

263
00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:03,670
We'll

264
00:12:03,900 --> 00:12:05,570
depart for

265
00:12:05,590 --> 00:12:06,340
Man Tribe tomorrow

266
00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:07,270
as planned.

267
00:12:09,510 --> 00:12:11,510
I'm not afraid of anyone.

268
00:12:12,950 --> 00:12:14,060
I'm afraid...

269
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:20,870
I'm afraid of Rou.

270
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:22,830
How's...

271
00:12:24,430 --> 00:12:26,110
How's Wen Rou doing?

272
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:28,990
Rou.

273
00:12:30,610 --> 00:12:32,010
It's such a long journey.

274
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:33,760
Why are you here?

275
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,540
You must be exhausted.

276
00:12:35,540 --> 00:12:36,470
Have some water.

277
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:37,390
Have you done

278
00:12:37,390 --> 00:12:38,590
what you promised me?

279
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:49,900
For General Zhennan,

280
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:51,100
we took a huge risk.

281
00:12:51,130 --> 00:12:52,070
Was it worth it?

282
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:53,900
Huo Jingheng

283
00:12:54,310 --> 00:12:56,570
is still sitting securely on his throne.

284
00:12:56,830 --> 00:12:59,230
Has his reign been shaken in
the slightest?

285
00:13:00,130 --> 00:13:01,060
Rou.

286
00:13:04,160 --> 00:13:06,110
Are you here to blame me?

287
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:12,190
I won't think of anything else

288
00:13:13,010 --> 00:13:14,670
until I've avenged my father.

289
00:13:15,970 --> 00:13:18,730
I should've stopped you back then!

290
00:13:19,250 --> 00:13:20,310
I never thought

291
00:13:20,350 --> 00:13:20,990
you'd actually

292
00:13:20,990 --> 00:13:22,910
settle in the palace.

293
00:13:23,490 --> 00:13:24,420
My Lord, My Lord.

294
00:13:24,710 --> 00:13:25,670
Stop drinking.

295
00:13:25,990 --> 00:13:27,920
We're setting off early tomorrow.

