409
00:18:03,790 --> 00:18:05,520
If not, you may leave the court.

410
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:07,090
Your Majesty!

411
00:18:08,620 --> 00:18:09,270
I

412
00:18:09,300 --> 00:18:11,300
