423
00:18:31,290 --> 00:18:32,890
There is one solution.

424
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:34,630
However…

425
00:18:34,650 --> 00:18:36,360
It concerns the destiny of Ning.

426
00:18:36,360 --> 00:18:37,320
Speak freely.

427
00:18:38,090 --> 00:18:39,950
According to astrology records,

428
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:42,170
to dispel this strange phenomenon,

429
00:18:42,170 --> 00:18:43,090
a concubine

430
00:18:43,110 --> 00:18:44,150
