433
00:18:48,460 --> 00:18:50,330
to Heaven every day

434
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:53,050
for 10 consecutive days.

435
00:18:55,190 --> 00:18:55,990
A concubine

436
00:18:56,830 --> 00:18:57,670
in my harem

437
00:18:57,710 --> 00:19:00,470
born at noon?

438
00:19:00,890 --> 00:19:01,450
I

439
00:19:01,470 --> 00:19:02,590
