00:20:21,710 --> 00:20:23,040
So, it relates

483
00:20:23,060 --> 00:20:25,410
to the people of the realm.

484
00:20:26,230 --> 00:20:26,820
As

485
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:28,460
the ruler of this country,

486
00:20:29,170 --> 00:20:30,650
