494
00:20:49,580 --> 00:20:51,180
Why is it her again?

495
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:53,650
Why is it her again?

496
00:21:01,580 --> 00:21:03,480
I heard that the court is discussing

497
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,350
