506
00:21:16,580 --> 00:21:17,910
Please grant me

507
00:21:17,970 --> 00:21:19,700
the title of consort now.

508
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:20,910
I'm willing to offer my blood

509
00:21:20,910 --> 00:21:22,310
to Heaven.

510
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:24,770
Is she crazy?

511
00:21:26,250 --> 00:21:27,630
What are you doing?

512
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:28,770
Your Highness,

513
00:21:28,770 --> 00:21:29,490
