514
00:21:29,490 --> 00:21:30,570
is a serious crime.

515
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:31,860
Then please, Your Majesty,

516
00:21:31,860 --> 00:21:33,480
execute me.

517
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:35,460
Then offer my entire body's blood

518
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:36,660
to Heaven.

519
00:21:36,810 --> 00:21:38,140
What Your Majesty likes

520
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:39,630
is what I like.

521
00:21:40,380 --> 00:21:41,840
I'm willing to give my life

522
00:21:41,900 --> 00:21:42,370
to protect

523
00:21:42,370 --> 00:21:43,900
the one Your Majesty loves.

524
00:21:47,020 --> 00:21:50,050
[Wanted]

525
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:51,000
Go.

526
00:21:54,030 --> 00:21:54,590
Go.

527
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:56,630
Raise your head.

528
00:21:58,750 --> 00:21:59,630
-Go.
