530
00:22:03,470 --> 00:22:04,590
-Go.
-Go.

531
00:22:08,950 --> 00:22:09,900
Go.

532
00:22:13,750 --> 00:22:14,510
Go.

533
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:36,200
Mr. Yi, you really

534
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:38,560
show up and disappear like a mystery.

535
00:22:40,730 --> 00:22:42,410
Your Highness, aren't you the same?

536
00:22:42,410 --> 00:22:45,290
Instead of returning to your land
while things were calm,

537
00:22:45,290 --> 00:22:47,140
