00:24:34,710 --> 00:24:35,350
Yue?

589
00:24:35,390 --> 00:24:35,990
Yue?

590
00:24:36,020 --> 00:24:36,590
Ling'er?

591
00:24:41,860 --> 00:24:43,400
This time, it should work.

592
00:24:43,530 --> 00:24:45,190
Rumor has it in the palace that

593
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:47,410
Consort Yue's miscarriage left her
so frail

594
00:24:47,410 --> 00:24:49,540
that she might not have much time left.

595
00:24:49,700 --> 00:24:50,590
Indeed.

596
00:24:51,100 --> 00:24:52,950
Everything outside the palace is arranged.

597
00:24:52,950 --> 00:24:53,910
In a few more days,

598
00:24:53,910 --> 00:24:55,100
the time will be just right.

599
00:24:55,100 --> 00:24:55,940
We must

600
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,560
get Ling'er out of the palace

601
00:24:57,850 --> 00:24:58,250
before

602
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:59,930
the Empress Dowager returns.

603
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:01,630
It was supposed to be simple—

604
00:25:01,860 --> 00:25:03,520
if it weren't for that Wen Rou.

605
00:25:04,750 --> 00:25:05,610
Do you think...

606
00:25:06,210 --> 00:25:07,380
she's really that close

607
00:25:07,380 --> 00:25:08,380
to Ling'er?

608
00:25:08,810 --> 00:25:09,870
Or does she...

609
00:25:10,390 --> 00:25:12,650
only like Ling'er because she likes you?

610
00:25:12,890 --> 00:25:13,690
Your Majesty!

611
00:25:14,590 --> 00:25:15,820
Your Majesty!

612
00:25:16,520 --> 00:25:17,410
Your Majesty.

613
00:25:17,770 --> 00:25:18,650
Wen Rou

614
00:25:18,790 --> 00:25:19,630
is practicing

615
00:25:19,660 --> 00:25:20,880
the Eightfold Vajra Technique

616
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:22,550
with Consort Yue.

617
00:25:29,230 --> 00:25:30,090
Straighten up.

618
00:25:31,650 --> 00:25:32,450
Bring it back.

619
00:25:37,690 --> 00:25:39,270
His Majesty is here!

620
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:42,000
My dear Ling'er.

621
00:25:43,050 --> 00:25:44,460
Your body is in such a state.

622
00:25:44,460 --> 00:25:46,690
How can you be out of bed and moving around?

623
00:25:46,690 --> 00:25:47,960
Your Majesty, please don't be angry.

624
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:48,980
I've already given Ling'er

625
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:49,750
many miraculous medicines

626
00:25:49,750 --> 00:25:50,800
from the Northern Commandery,

627
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:51,810
specially to treat

628
00:25:51,810 --> 00:25:53,270
weakness after miscarriage.

629
00:25:53,270 --> 00:25:54,740
After several doses,

630
00:25:54,870 --> 00:25:55,550
look how rosy

631
00:25:55,550 --> 00:25:56,950
her complexion is now.

632
00:25:56,980 --> 00:25:57,560
I have invited

633
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:59,080
several imperial physicians,

634
00:25:59,080 --> 00:26:01,340
and they all say her health is excellent.

635
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:04,190
Consort Yue,

636
00:26:05,740 --> 00:26:06,500
are you...

637
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:09,160
really feeling better?

638
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:10,680
I...

639
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:15,990
truly am.

640
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:19,800
Well then,

641
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:21,120
thank you.

642
00:26:22,010 --> 00:26:23,480
I will surely take good care

643
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:25,080
of your beloved.

644
00:26:25,470 --> 00:26:27,050
My sincerity

645
00:26:27,330 --> 00:26:29,010
can be witnessed by the sun and moon—

646
00:26:29,010 --> 00:26:30,000
I only hope

647
00:26:30,020 --> 00:26:31,370
you can see it too.

648
00:26:38,470 --> 00:26:39,170
Rou,

649
00:26:39,340 --> 00:26:40,330
there's one more thing.

650
00:26:40,330 --> 00:26:41,260
Well,

651
00:26:42,050 --> 00:26:42,850
the one

652
00:26:42,990 --> 00:26:44,200
who used to impersonate Consort Yue

653
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,340
was Yue Chi.

654
00:26:47,430 --> 00:26:49,720
It seems Ling'er's repeated encounters
with danger

655
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:51,650
were all secretly plotted by them,

656
00:26:51,750 --> 00:26:53,980
but I unexpectedly foiled
their plans each time.

657
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:55,260
I can't let Ling'er—

658
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:57,310
Consort Yue—

659
00:26:57,310 --> 00:26:58,440
just die so lightly.

660
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:07,120
Something's not right.

661
00:27:07,370 --> 00:27:09,140
There's something wrong with this Wen Rou.

662
00:27:09,140 --> 00:27:10,260
I think so too.

663
00:27:11,470 --> 00:27:12,430
I've already arranged for someone

664
00:27:12,430 --> 00:27:13,360
to investigate.

665
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:15,030
Now,

666
00:27:15,260 --> 00:27:17,000
it's too soon to draw conclusions.

667
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:17,880
It seems the trick

668
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:19,150
of making her die of illness

669
00:27:19,150 --> 00:27:21,150
inside the palace won't work anymore.

670
00:27:21,150 --> 00:27:21,980
My mother

671
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:23,290
will return from worshipping

672
00:27:23,290 --> 00:27:25,330
at Cheng'en Temple in three days.

673
00:27:26,670 --> 00:27:27,870
I have an idea,

674
00:27:29,070 --> 00:27:30,200
but it's a bit risky.

675
00:27:31,210 --> 00:27:32,140
Tell me.

676
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:34,740
Dying from illness takes time

677
00:27:35,110 --> 00:27:37,070
and can easily lead to complications.

678
00:27:37,070 --> 00:27:38,740
Why not make it a sudden death instead?

679
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:39,690
A sudden death?

680
00:27:40,670 --> 00:27:42,670
It should not happen inside the palace.

681
00:27:42,670 --> 00:27:43,450
That way,

682
00:27:43,830 --> 00:27:45,110
the problem of Consort Yue's body

683
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:46,370
can be easily handled.

684
00:27:46,410 --> 00:27:47,860
I will just arrange for the guards

685
00:27:47,860 --> 00:27:48,520
to say

686
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:50,570
the body is missing.

687
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:51,800
I just

688
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:53,070
haven't figured out

689
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:54,430
what reason to use

690
00:27:54,450 --> 00:27:55,960
to get Ling'er out of the palace yet.

691
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:58,290
It's best if there are many people around.

692
00:27:58,990 --> 00:28:00,150
You just said

693
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,170
the Empress Dowager will return from

694
00:28:02,170 --> 00:28:03,870
Cheng'en Temple three days later, right?

695
00:28:03,870 --> 00:28:05,870
That's after the Lantern Festival?

696
00:28:06,190 --> 00:28:07,120
Yes.

697
00:28:07,620 --> 00:28:08,710
By tradition,

698
00:28:09,360 --> 00:28:10,750
my mother prays for the country

699
00:28:10,750 --> 00:28:12,060
at Cheng'en Temple

700
00:28:12,150 --> 00:28:13,550
every Lantern Festival.

701
00:28:15,870 --> 00:28:16,270
Isn't this

702
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:18,270
a perfect and natural opportunity?

703
00:28:28,170 --> 00:28:28,930
Rou.

704
00:28:30,230 --> 00:28:31,280
Rou, come.

705
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:33,720
Sit down.

706
00:28:39,930 --> 00:28:40,690
Rou.

707
00:28:42,770 --> 00:28:43,920
You've lost weight.

708
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:47,790
I'll get straight to the point.

709
00:28:47,790 --> 00:28:49,210
Tomorrow is the Lantern Festival.

710
00:28:49,210 --> 00:28:50,360
The Emperor will take the harem

711
00:28:50,360 --> 00:28:52,790
to Cheng'en Temple
to meet the Empress Dowager.

712
00:28:52,790 --> 00:28:53,590
At night, they will

713
00:28:53,590 --> 00:28:55,190
release Kongming lanterns
on Lingshou Mountain

714
00:28:55,190 --> 00:28:55,820
outside the temple

715
00:28:55,820 --> 00:28:57,150
to pray for the country.

716
00:28:57,390 --> 00:28:58,790
That's quite a big event.

717
00:29:01,660 --> 00:29:03,390
The reason sounds legitimate.

718
00:29:03,460 --> 00:29:05,460
It sounds like Huo Jingheng's idea.

719
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,930
But the idea is quite twisted.

720
00:29:08,190 --> 00:29:10,080
I guess Yue Chi suggested it.

721
00:29:10,590 --> 00:29:11,350
They probably want to cause an accident

722
00:29:11,350 --> 00:29:13,350
to have Consort Yue suddenly die.

723
00:29:13,390 --> 00:29:14,590
I'll stay alert.

724
00:29:15,740 --> 00:29:16,500
No.

725
00:29:17,650 --> 00:29:18,150
This is

726
00:29:18,180 --> 00:29:20,040
a rare golden opportunity for us.

727
00:29:20,050 --> 00:29:22,050
We need to turn defense into offense

728
00:29:22,520 --> 00:29:23,840
and make a scene

729
00:29:24,080 --> 00:29:25,610
to liven up the atmosphere.

730
00:29:26,100 --> 00:29:27,230
Prime Minister Yue,

731
00:29:27,320 --> 00:29:30,130
Cheng'en Temple is,
after all, a Buddhist temple.

732
00:29:30,240 --> 00:29:30,640
[Cheng'en Temple]

733
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:31,840
Painting it like this

734
00:29:31,870 --> 00:29:34,070
feels a bit disrespectful, doesn't it?

735
00:29:36,330 --> 00:29:37,530
These are people?

736
00:29:38,170 --> 00:29:39,490
[Cheng'en Temple]

737
00:29:39,490 --> 00:29:40,350
The position for

738
00:29:40,350 --> 00:29:43,530
releasing the Kongming lanterns
seems a bit off, doesn't it?

739
00:29:43,530 --> 00:29:44,310
trees, trees.

740
00:29:44,310 --> 00:29:45,030
trees, trees.

741
00:29:45,030 --> 00:29:45,960
These are trees.

742
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:47,950
Just make do with it.

743
00:29:49,280 --> 00:29:50,340
Trees?

744
00:29:52,190 --> 00:29:53,650
At five tomorrow morning,

745
00:29:53,690 --> 00:29:55,400
Your Majesty will lead the concubines

746
00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:56,600
out of the palace

747
00:29:56,770 --> 00:29:58,430
to Cheng'en Temple.

748
00:29:59,410 --> 00:30:00,850
I'll follow shortly after,

749
00:30:00,850 --> 00:30:01,610
take a shortcut,

750
00:30:01,610 --> 00:30:03,260
and go to the temple alone.

751
00:30:04,990 --> 00:30:06,300
At 11 a.m., Your Majesty

752
00:30:06,300 --> 00:30:06,510
[Wetuo Hall]

753
00:30:06,510 --> 00:30:08,030
will arrive at Cheng'en Temple
with the concubines

754
00:30:08,030 --> 00:30:09,590
to meet the Empress Dowager.

755
00:30:09,590 --> 00:30:11,320
By then, I'll already be there,

756
00:30:14,430 --> 00:30:16,130
disguised as a temple servant,

757
00:30:16,130 --> 00:30:17,990
waiting in the firewood room.

758
00:30:19,210 --> 00:30:20,120
At 5 p.m.,

759
00:30:20,220 --> 00:30:21,620
while everyone is resting,

760
00:30:21,620 --> 00:30:22,900
Ling'er will sneak into the firewood room

761
00:30:22,900 --> 00:30:24,430
and switch clothes with me.

762
00:30:30,510 --> 00:30:31,320
At 7 p.m.,

763
00:30:31,410 --> 00:30:32,960
Your Majesty will lead the concubines

764
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:33,870
to release Kongming lanterns

765
00:30:33,870 --> 00:30:35,640
on Lingshou Mountain next to the temple.

766
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:37,090
By that time, it'll be dark.

767
00:30:37,090 --> 00:30:39,840
I just need to keep my head down
and walk through the crowd.

768
00:30:39,840 --> 00:30:40,920
If anyone asks,

769
00:30:41,320 --> 00:30:44,320
I'll say my face
is having an allergic reaction again.

770
00:30:47,710 --> 00:30:49,220
Then I'll pretend to slip

771
00:30:49,250 --> 00:30:50,510
and fall off the cliff.

772
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:52,670
Consort Yue!

773
00:30:52,670 --> 00:30:53,600
Consort Yue!

774
00:30:57,420 --> 00:30:58,540
Consort Yue!

775
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:01,040
Consort Yue will appear to die on the spot.

776
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:02,470
But in reality, I'll use my lightness skill

777
00:31:02,470 --> 00:31:03,270
to glide to a lower ledge

778
00:31:03,270 --> 00:31:04,510
beneath the cliff.

779
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:07,560
Lingshou Mountain is thick with trees,

780
00:31:07,560 --> 00:31:09,020
so I'll hide beneath them.

781
00:31:11,240 --> 00:31:12,020
By then, Ling'er will

782
00:31:12,020 --> 00:31:12,770
already have been taken down the mountain

783
00:31:12,770 --> 00:31:13,650
by Wei Zhang.

784
00:31:13,780 --> 00:31:14,820
Have you

785
00:31:15,280 --> 00:31:16,300
asked Ling'er about this?

786
00:31:16,300 --> 00:31:17,140
Did she agree?

787
00:31:17,340 --> 00:31:18,020
She didn't.

788
00:31:18,540 --> 00:31:19,670
I asked her once too,

789
00:31:20,120 --> 00:31:21,180
but it didn't help.

790
00:31:21,650 --> 00:31:22,290
Then...

791
00:31:23,050 --> 00:31:25,450
we'll just have to make her unhappy for now.

792
00:31:25,850 --> 00:31:27,140
You mean…

793
00:31:28,120 --> 00:31:29,030
Knock her out.

794
00:31:33,220 --> 00:31:34,180
Knock her out?

795
00:31:35,100 --> 00:31:36,230
Who's going to do it?

796
00:31:54,010 --> 00:31:55,070
In past years,

797
00:31:55,090 --> 00:31:56,590
I always prayed for the country
and the people

798
00:31:56,590 --> 00:31:59,060
by myself on this day.

799
00:31:59,180 --> 00:32:00,610
Today,

800
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:02,260
the Emperor had the concubines

801
00:32:02,260 --> 00:32:03,590
pray with me.

802
00:32:03,870 --> 00:32:05,090
If the gods knew,

803
00:32:05,090 --> 00:32:05,910
[Peaceful Land, Prosperous People]

804
00:32:05,910 --> 00:32:07,110
it must be because

805
00:32:07,140 --> 00:32:08,780
our sincerity moved them.

806
00:32:08,990 --> 00:32:10,550
Your Grace, you're merciful.

807
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:12,350
Your Majesty, you're merciful.

808
00:32:34,580 --> 00:32:35,850
Don't come any closer.

809
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:38,290
What is this troublemaker up to now?

810
00:32:49,770 --> 00:32:50,730
Everyone

811
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:51,300
stay where you are.

812
00:32:51,300 --> 00:32:52,350
Don't move around.

813
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:53,450
Everyone's position

814
00:32:53,450 --> 00:32:54,080
was calculated in advance

815
00:32:54,080 --> 00:32:55,880
based on their birth charts.

816
00:32:55,910 --> 00:32:57,240
Moving around randomly

817
00:32:57,290 --> 00:32:58,750
will disrupt the praying.

818
00:33:01,590 --> 00:33:04,210
I've been on to you, you little rascal.

819
00:33:17,470 --> 00:33:18,320
Snake!

820
00:33:18,590 --> 00:33:19,420
Snake!

821
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:21,120
-No! No!
-I'm so scared!

822
00:33:21,180 --> 00:33:21,670
Ling'er!

823
00:33:21,670 --> 00:33:23,200
-I'm scared too!
-Ling'er!

824
00:33:23,750 --> 00:33:25,610
Where are you putting your hands?

825
00:33:33,950 --> 00:33:34,990
Ling'er,

826
00:33:35,020 --> 00:33:35,900
how did you…

827
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:47,110
Prime Minister Yue?

828
00:33:47,560 --> 00:33:48,730
How is it you?

829
00:33:49,620 --> 00:33:51,910
Why did Prime Minister Yue
impersonate Consort Yue?

830
00:33:51,910 --> 00:33:52,750
Could it be...

831
00:33:52,790 --> 00:33:53,950
Consort Yue who's been
in the palace all along

832
00:33:53,950 --> 00:33:56,030
is actually Prime Minister Yue?

833
00:33:59,060 --> 00:34:00,080
What a farce.

834
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:01,960
How festive indeed.

835
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,460
Is it too late

836
00:34:07,270 --> 00:34:08,929
to jump off the cliff?

837
00:34:09,520 --> 00:34:11,000
How could this happen?

838
00:34:26,429 --> 00:34:27,550
Be quiet.

839
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:29,210
You're making me dizzy.

840
00:34:31,909 --> 00:34:32,840
I'm not in the mood

841
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:33,920
to draw

842
00:34:33,949 --> 00:34:35,810
those useless charms like you do.

843
00:34:40,110 --> 00:34:40,630
Rou.

844
00:34:40,889 --> 00:34:41,460
Rou.

845
00:34:42,230 --> 00:34:43,429
Are you alright?

846
00:34:43,810 --> 00:34:44,790
Did you get hurt?

847
00:34:45,850 --> 00:34:47,110
If she were hurt,

848
00:34:47,420 --> 00:34:48,880
would she show up tonight?

849
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:53,630
I'm just

850
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:55,230
worried about Rou's safety.

851
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,590
With the Crown Prince and your plan

852
00:34:57,590 --> 00:34:59,070
being so meticulous,

853
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:00,860
what is there to worry about?

854
00:35:01,900 --> 00:35:02,750
I suppose the Emperor

855
00:35:02,750 --> 00:35:04,100
hasn't made any decision yet.

856
00:35:04,100 --> 00:35:05,360
But it doesn't matter.

857
00:35:06,750 --> 00:35:08,530
I have already spread the news

858
00:35:08,550 --> 00:35:09,150
that Consort Yue

859
00:35:09,150 --> 00:35:10,950
is actually Yue Chi in disguise.

860
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:12,940
He was exposed

861
00:35:12,970 --> 00:35:14,170
in front of everyone.

862
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:16,170
By tomorrow, the taverns and teahouses

863
00:35:16,170 --> 00:35:17,540
will be buzzing.

864
00:35:18,350 --> 00:35:19,620
From now on, Prime Minister Yue

865
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:21,170
will have to keep a low profile.

866
00:35:21,170 --> 00:35:23,630
As for the Empress Dowager
and Huo Jingheng,

867
00:35:25,130 --> 00:35:26,990
they're about to have a big fight.

868
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:38,150
[Diligent from Dawn to Dusk]

869
00:35:38,150 --> 00:35:39,150
Your Grace! Your Grace!

870
00:35:39,150 --> 00:35:39,810
Your Grace!

871
00:35:39,950 --> 00:35:40,910
His Majesty has arrived.

872
00:35:40,910 --> 00:35:42,510
He's just outside the gates.

873
00:35:44,270 --> 00:35:45,520
Hurry!

874
00:35:55,720 --> 00:35:57,150
Who brought

875
00:35:57,190 --> 00:35:58,450
